title: Youth unemployment rate in Ghana in 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Youth unemployment rate, containing a total of 21 data points.
Overall Youth unemployment rate has decreased over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2003 and 2004.
Maximum Youth unemployment rate, about 16.26 was reported at Year 2000
The lowest Youth unemployment rate, of value 9.31 was reported at Year 2006
